Aurora Studio - Portable Build Notice
======================================
Version: 0.1.0
Build type: Windows portable folder

---

This is an early local desktop build of Aurora Studio for development and
smoke testing purposes. It is not a production release.

---

No Provider Keys Bundled
------------------------

This build does not contain any provider API keys, credentials, or tokens.
No OpenAI, Anthropic, RunwayML, ElevenLabs, or other provider credentials
are included in this bundle.

The application makes no network calls or AI model requests.

---

No Plugin Execution Enabled
----------------------------

This build does not execute plugin code.
Plugin metadata may be registered and displayed, but no plugin modules
are loaded or executed at runtime.

---

No Database Bundled
-------------------

This build does not include a database engine.
All application state is held in memory during the session.
State may be saved and loaded using bundle JSON files selected by the user.

---

No Warranty
-----------

This is a smoke build provided for local testing only.
It is not suitable for production use.
No warranty is provided.

